DECISION EFFICIENCY FORMULA:
DE = (Success_Rate * 0.4) + (Survival_Rate * 0.3) + (Score_Factor * 0.2) + (Speed_Factor * 0.1)
Where:
+ Success_Rate: Percentage of missions completed successfully (0-1)
+ Survival_Rate: Percentage of games where agent didn't die (0-1)
+ Score_Factor: min(Average_Score/1000, 1) - normalized score performance
+ Speed_Factor: min(1000/Average_Steps, 1) - rewards efficiency
